                      <span>5</span>
                    </span>
                    의 크기 비교하기
                  </h3>
                  <div class="question_box">
                    <div class="pop_inn">
                        <div class="method_tit">
                          <div class="tag">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" viewBox="0 0 115 40" fill="none">
